title: [Willow Walk]
description: As the trail zigzags through dense growths of willow trees, it becomes more clearly delineated, changing from rough gravel to smooth river stones skillfully laid in a handsome pattern.  Over the tree line above, the gables of a large building can be seen, the rich sienna of its timbers peeking through the silvery green of the willow branches in places.  A small sign stands next to the paving stones of the path.

As the trail zigzags through dense growths of willow trees, it becomes more clearly delineated, changing from rough gravel to smooth river stones skillfully laid in a handsome pattern.  Over the tree line above, the gables of a large building can be glimpsed in the bright moonlight, the rich sienna of its timbers peeking through the silver-grey of the willow branches in places.  A small sign stands next to the paving stones of the path.
